                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Sarah, I've heard you're working on a cure. Can you tell me more?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "Yes, I've been studying the infection. But I'm afraid I've become infected myself. I need your help to finish the cure."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "What do you need me to do?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "sarah",
                    "line": "I need you to find a way to restore power to the laboratory. Without it, I won't be able to finish the cure."
