                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Anne, I need your help. I'm trying to figure out what's going on in this village."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "What do you mean? The outbreak, the zombies? It's chaos out there."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "I think there's more to it. Someone or something is pulling the strings. Have you noticed anything unusual?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "Now that you mention it, there have been some strange occurrences. Tools gone missing, food supplies disappearing. But I haven't seen anything that would suggest someone is in control of all this."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 3,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "store",
